        {"$GMRTextItem":"v3","%Name":"text_74B645EB","alignment":0,"charSpacing":0.0,"colour":4283809600,"fontId":{"name":"fnt_Title","path":"fonts/fnt_Title/fnt_Title.yy",},"frameH":40.0,"frameW":600.0,"frozen":false,"ignore":false,"inheritedItemId":null,"inheritItemSettings":false,"lineSpacing":0.0,"name":"text_74B645EB","paragraphSpacing":0.0,"resourceType":"GMRTextItem","resourceVersion":"2.0","rotation":0.0,"scaleX":1.0,"scaleY":1.0,"text":"ABOUT STREWT","wrap":true,"x":340.0,"y":20.0,},
        {"$GMRTextItem":"v3","%Name":"text_531302","alignment":0,"charSpacing":0.0,"colour":4294967295,"fontId":{"name":"fnt_Info","path":"fonts/fnt_Info/fnt_Info.yy",},"frameH":600.0,"frameW":920.0,"frozen":false,"ignore":false,"inheritedItemId":null,"inheritItemSettings":false,"lineSpacing":0.0,"name":"text_531302","paragraphSpacing":0.0,"resourceType":"GMRTextItem","resourceVersion":"2.0","rotation":0.0,"scaleX":1.0,"scaleY":1.0,"text":"Strewt - or the String Reading & Writing library - provides utilities for reading and writing text in GameMaker.\r\n\r\nThe \"Table parser\" and \"BBCode parser\" demonstrations showcase the reading functionality.\r\nThe \"Table formatter\" and \"Indented object formatter\" demonstrations showcase the writing functionality.\r\n\r\nIn each demonstration, there are a couple built-in examples prepared - for correct and error cases alike (when applicable). Additionally, you may load a custom file for processing (this functionality is disabled in web build).\r\n\r\nTo learn more, you can see the reading and writing guides, or visit the repository website and check the underlying code. The website also has the GameMaker package and the installation guide.","wrap":true,"x":340.0,"y":80.0,},
